<ul>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601&amp;id=c243284e46&amp;e=467ab44f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601%26id%3Dc243284e46%26e%3D467ab44f23&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587483740927000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHHUcpQ6ndQ-YYr6PdeV3N1q0ZyBg">Transparent Classroom</a></strong>: please update ALL contact information (including your sharing preferences).</li>
<li>
<u><strong>#ECMSathome</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Share photos and videos on social media using our hashtag. This is a space for everyone to share what learning looks like at home. This can be working on Google Classroom, gardening, special projects, actions of the week…anything!</li>
<li>
<strong>Share some gratitude!</strong> During this difficult moment, being grateful is incredibly important. It heals us, it sends love into our community, and it allows us to see the moments of positivity and possibility! We have a staff tradition of sharing gratitudes among ourselves every week, and we would like to include you in this tradition! Think of who has made your week bright and acknowledge them. <strong>Please submit your gratitudes anytime <a href="https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601&amp;id=d4ac1921c4&amp;e=467ab44f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601%26id%3Dd4ac1921c4%26e%3D467ab44f23&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587483740927000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEUhWSE_1Vg3prUR94Dv5ankq8fCg">HERE</a>.</strong>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Technology Support &amp; Access</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<strong><u>Tech Support/Access</u></strong>: Reach out to Mr. Dave if you need support accessing technology. If you’d be interested in workshops around how to use IXL/Lexia, how to do a Hangout/Zoom call, etc, let him know!</li>
<li>
<u><strong>K-5 Families</strong></u>: We know that juggling devices in homes can be a challenge. If there were more devices (ex. Chromebooks, tablets) from ECMS available, would that help your child(ren) to engage with their school work? If so, please email <a href="mailto:david.weinreb@elmcitymontessori.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">david.weinreb@<wbr></wbr>elmcitymontessori.org</a>.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
<div>
<p><strong>NHPS Distribution of Meals</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>New Haven Public Schools (NHPS) meal distribution sites are open as Grab-and-Go sites <strong>Monday, Wednesday, and Friday, 9:00 AM -12:00 PM, </strong>for the duration of the public schools’ closure. <a href="https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601&amp;id=323b560415&amp;e=467ab44f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601%26id%3D323b560415%26e%3D467ab44f23&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587483740927000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFpoN29TO9YY6l_xFsaX63fzOTVFQ">Here is a link </a>to meal distribution sites.</li>
<li>Click on the following link for a food assistance resource guide issued by the City of New Haven, 2-1-1, the Connecticut Food Bank, and CARE Research. (<a href="https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601&amp;id=2887310a10&amp;e=467ab44f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601%26id%3D2887310a10%26e%3D467ab44f23&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587483740927000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEhvUPgqdrUdpBrTlKwiTC93yDQ9A">English</a>/<a href="https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601&amp;id=6e09924d89&amp;e=467ab44f23" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://elmcitymontessori.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D45e80f4ec8c11bf33c4156601%26id%3D6e09924d89%26e%3D467ab44f23&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1587483740927000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGJKmuM2fdrUiWVB0aZngLN16hCmQ">español</a>)</li>
